      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET AGRIPPINA (1) is generally an honest type in the frame at eight of 22 starts but missed the placings last time when eighth (23.20) over 400m at this track. Performs well off this draw. Has the inside draw and looks tough to beat. BLUE AND BOUJEE (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 22.57 beating NALAH PATANGA. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Sure to measure up. HELL BENT (6) has a strong record here with five wins and five placings from 12 starts. In the money last time at this track (22.63) in a Grade 5, finishing a one length third. Among the main chances. ZATARA STORM (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
